== Overview == Beings born in this heaven transform their sensory objects (五境) into realms of pleasure. The celestial beings in this heaven are described as having a height of 2.5 ''ri'' (approximately 10 kilometers), constantly emitting light, and living for 8,000 celestial years, with one day and night in this realm equating to 800 human years. It is said that when males and females face each other and laugh, the purpose of sexual union is fulfilled. Offspring are born through spontaneous generation on the laps of the parents and are described as resembling 12-year-old human children in size{{要出典|date=2018th year 2月27日 (火) 08:11 (UTC)|title=}}.
